        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Preventing Termination of Utility Services in Bankruptcy Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends federal bankruptcy law to specify that an individual debtor may not be required to furnish a security deposit to maintain utility services&nbsp;if the debtor pays specified debts owed to the utility within a certain timeframe.</p>]]></text>
